Package: qtlApp
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-01
Title: AttieLab QTL Viewer — Interactive Shiny App for Diversity Outbred Mouse QTL Analysis
Description: A modular R/Shiny web application for exploring quantitative trait
    loci (QTL) in Diversity Outbred mouse data. Provides genome-wide LOD scans,
    Manhattan and cis/trans plots, peak exploration with founder allele
    effects, sex- and diet-stratified comparisons with on-the-fly difference
    plots, trait search across large genomic datasets, correlation, profile
    plots, mediation analysis, and SNP association. Designed for deployment on
    Posit Connect or a Docker host with optional S3-backed data storage.
